st-assistant-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-response-1235033146/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">滚石乐队</a></em>的一份声明中做出了回应，称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dismisses-sexual-harassment-allegations-against-him-as-baseless-announces-plans-to-countersue-for-sexual-coercion-3762636">Pisciotta的指控为“毫无根据”，并宣布他计划进行反击</a>。</p><p>同时，前伴侣朱莉娅·福克斯（Julia Fox）在最近的一次采访中承认，她对与韦斯特的关系感到遗憾， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julia-fox-shares-regret-on-dating-kanye-west-i-was-being-used-as-a-pawn-3802547">她说这使她处于“我一生中最不舒服的位置”</a> 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adidas-to-receive-e100million-boost-after-settling-with-kanye-west-after-years-of-lawsuits-3807538">多年的诉讼后，阿迪达斯邮政与坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）定居后，将获得1亿欧元的提升</a>。</p> ;
